      <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

      <div class="container marketing">

        <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/centreIcon.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>New Meditation Centre</h2>
            <p>
              Our goal is to acquire a new facility with the permission for Religious Assembly so that we can resume our meditation programs, Dhamma discussions, children's programs, mindfulness programs, stress relief programs, counselling, retreats and daily sermons without a hindrance.
            </p>

            <!--<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#section1" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>-->
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/savingsIcon.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>Financial Status</h2>
            <p>
              It takes about a minimum investment of 1.5 million dollars to aquire a new facility with proper bylaw permissions. At the moment, we can get about $500,000 for this by selling the current property of the centre and another $300,000 as a loan from the bank. The remaining $700,000 needs to be raised.
            </p>
            <!--<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#section2" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p> -->
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="rounded-circle" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/projectlogoIcon.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>Development Fund</h2>
            <p>
              We have setup a Meditation Centre Development Fund to cover the shortfall of $700,000. We kindly request the devotees of our centre, as well as other organizations and the generous donors around the world, to contrinute to this fund and assist us fill this shortfall. Much merits for your support! 
            </p>
            <!--<p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#section3" role="button" target="_top">View details &raquo;</a></p>-->
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        </div><!-- /.row -->


        <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <a name="section1"></a>
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Meditation Centre Development<span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 d-md-none">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto feature-visual" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/centre.jpg" alt="New Meditation Centre Image">
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-7">
            <p class="lead">
              We have relocated part of our public programs and suspended others in due respect to an order given by The City of Edmonton to cease public services offered at our current facility due to bylaw restrictions. 
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
              Our goal is to purchase or build a facility in a location where we have the permission for Religious Assembly so that we can resume our meditation programs, Dhamma discussions, children's programs, youth programs, mindfulness development programs, stress relief programs, counselling, retreats and daily sermons, etc. that we offered, without any hindrance. We also want to ensure that there is sufficient space available for hosting our annual religious, cultural and community programs in it.
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
               Purchase of a this kind of facility is much more financially challenging than buying a residential place. However, we are confident that this challenge can be overcome, and allow this meditation centre to continue its public service, thanking to the commitment and generosity of the local and global community.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 d-none d-md-block">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto feature-visual" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/centre.jpg" alt="New Meditation Centre Image">
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <a name="section2"></a>
            <h2 id="section2" class="featurette-heading">Financial Status Overview<span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1 feature-visual d-md-none">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/savings.jpg" alt="Financial Status Image">
          </div>          
          <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
            <p class="lead">
              In current market conditions, it requires about a minimum investment of 1.5 million dollars to purchase or build a suitable facility for the meditation centre in a location where there is permission for Religious Assembly. Towards this, we can allocate about $500,000 by selling the current house where the meditation centre is established at, and also obtain loan of about $300,000 from the bank. This leaves a <span class="font-weight-bold">shortfall of about $700,000</span>. 
            </p>
            <p class="lead">
              To cover this shortfall, we have established a Meditation Centre Development Fund and started obtaining pledges from our devotees and well wishers. Contributions made to this fund will solely be used for the establishment of the new meditation centre facility. We kindly request the generous people in Edmonton, across Canada and the World, to come forward and assist us in this difficult but noble mission. 
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1 feature-visual d-none d-md-block">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/savings.jpg" alt="Financial Status Image">
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

        <div class="row featurette">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <a name="section3"></a>
            <h2 id="section3" class="featurette-heading">Development Fund Contributions<span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 d-md-none" style="text-align:center;">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto feature-visual" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/projectlogo.png" alt="Fund Contributions Image" style="width:340px;">
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-7">
            <p class="lead">
              Your generosity is the only source of funding available to save this meditation centre. Please help this meritorius deed and inform your commitment by email to <a href="mailto:president@abva.org">president@abva.org</a> or by contacting the Meditation Centre at 780-641-9795.
            </p>
            <p class="lead"> 
              As a registered, charitable, non-profit organization, we will provide you <span class="font-weight-bold">Official Tax Receipts</span> for your donation. You may use the <a href="http://www.cra-arc.gc.ca/chrts-gvng/dnrs/svngs/clmng1b2-eng.html" target="_blank"><span class="font-weight-bold">Charitable Donation Tax Credit Calculator</span></a> of the Canada Revenue Agency to see how much tax credit you will be entitled to receive based on the total annual charitable donations you make.
            </p>
            <p class="lead"> 
              The following chart shows the growth of the Meditation Centre Development Fund in real time. We are thankful to the donors who already expressed their commitments and we hubly ask you also to consider helping this worthy cause.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 d-none d-md-block" style="text-align:center;">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto feature-visual" src="https://abvasvmc.github.io/capital/projectlogo.png" alt="Fund Contributions Image" style="width:340px;">
          </div>

